tulip fever is an upcoming historical drama film directed by justin chadwick and written by sir tom stoppard , adapted from a novel by deborah &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it stars alicia vikander , dane dehaan , zach galifianakis , judi dench , christoph waltz , jack o'connell , holliday grainger , matthew morrison and cara delevingne . the plot follows a 17th-century painter in amsterdam who falls in love with a married woman of whom he has been hired to draw a portrait . the film is set to be released in the united states on august 25 , 2017 , by the weinstein company .